{
  "video_id": "_bm98rrVZzE",
  "title": "How the military fights climate change | David Titley",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12833.0,
      "end_time": 16656.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;d like to tell you a story about climate and change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16680.0,
      "end_time": 19346.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s really a story about people and not polar bears."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20640.0,
      "end_time": 24176.0,
      "text": "So this is our house that we lived in in the mid-2000s."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24200.0,
      "end_time": 28976.0,
      "text": "I was the chief operating officer for the Navy&#39;s weather and ocean service."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29000.0,
      "end_time": 31896.0,
      "text": "It happened to be down at a place called Stennis Space Center"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31920.0,
      "end_time": 33176.0,
      "text": "right on the Gulf Coast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33200.0,
      "end_time": 35915.0,
      "text": "so we lived in a little town called Waveland, Mississippi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35939.0,
      "end_time": 39456.0,
      "text": "nice modest house, and as you can see, it&#39;s up against a storm surge."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39480.0,
      "end_time": 42135.0,
      "text": "Now, if you ever wonder"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42160.0,
      "end_time": 45616.0,
      "text": "what a 30-foot or nine-meter storm surge does"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45640.0,
      "end_time": 47696.0,
      "text": "coming up your street,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47720.0,
      "end_time": 49336.0,
      "text": "let me show you."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49360.0,
      "end_time": 50696.0,
      "text": "Same house."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50720.0,
      "end_time": 54256.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s me, kind of wondering what&#39;s next."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54280.0,
      "end_time": 57776.0,
      "text": "But when we say we lost our house -- this is, like, right after Katrina --"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57800.0,
      "end_time": 61616.0,
      "text": "so the house is either all the way up there in the railway tracks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61640.0,
      "end_time": 64456.0,
      "text": "or it&#39;s somewhere down there in the Gulf of Mexico,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64480.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66656.0,
      "text": "and to this day, we really, we lost our house."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66680.0,
      "end_time": 67936.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t know where it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67960.0,
      "end_time": 69216.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69240.0,
      "end_time": 71950.0,
      "text": "You know, it&#39;s gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71120.0,
      "end_time": 76160.0,
      "text": "So I don&#39;t show this for pity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76400.0,
      "end_time": 80456.0,
      "text": "because in many ways, we were the luckiest people on the Gulf Coast."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80480.0,
      "end_time": 83336.0,
      "text": "One of the things is, we had insurance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83360.0,
      "end_time": 87776.0,
      "text": "and that idea of insurance is probably pretty important there."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87800.0,
      "end_time": 90735.0,
      "text": "But does this scale up, you know, what happened here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90760.0,
      "end_time": 94160.0,
      "text": "And I think it kind of does, because as you&#39;ve heard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94400.0,
      "end_time": 95736.0,
      "text": "as the sea levels come up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95760.0,
      "end_time": 99656.0,
      "text": "it takes weaker and weaker storms to do something like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 99680.0,
      "end_time": 103576.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s just step back for a second and kind of look at this."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103600.0,
      "end_time": 106175.0,
      "text": "And, you know, climate&#39;s really complicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106200.0,
      "end_time": 108976.0,
      "text": "a lot of moving parts in this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109000.0,
      "end_time": 111896.0,
      "text": "but I kind of put it about it&#39;s all about the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111920.0,
      "end_time": 115296.0,
      "text": "See, see those three blue dots there down on the lower part?"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115320.0,
      "end_time": 118616.0,
      "text": "The one you can easily see, that&#39;s all the water in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118640.0,
      "end_time": 122960.0,
      "text": "Those two smaller dots, those are the fresh water."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122120.0,
      "end_time": 125456.0,
      "text": "And it turns out that as the climate changes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125480.0,
      "end_time": 128976.0,
      "text": "the distribution of that water is changing very fundamentally."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 129000.0,
      "end_time": 132736.0,
      "text": "So now we have too much, too little, wrong place, wrong time."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 132760.0,
      "end_time": 137335.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s salty where it should be fresh; it&#39;s liquid where it should be frozen;"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 137360.0,
      "end_time": 138936.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s wet where it should be dry;"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 138960.0,
      "end_time": 142735.0,
      "text": "and in fact, the very chemistry of the ocean itself is changing."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142759.0,
      "end_time": 147696.0,
      "text": "And what that does from a security or a military part"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147720.0,
      "end_time": 149976.0,
      "text": "is it does three things:"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150000.0,
      "end_time": 153576.0,
      "text": "it changes the very operating environment that we&#39;re working in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 153600.0,
      "end_time": 155176.0,
      "text": "it threatens our bases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155200.0,
      "end_time": 158696.0,
      "text": "and then it has geostrategic risks, which sounds kind of fancy"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 158720.0,
      "end_time": 161976.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ll explain what I mean by that in a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 162000.0,
      "end_time": 165496.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s go to just a couple examples here."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 165520.0,
      "end_time": 167736.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ll start off with what we all know"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 167760.0,
      "end_time": 170935.0,
      "text": "is of course a political and humanitarian catastrophe"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 170960.0,
      "end_time": 172376.0,
      "text": "that is Syria."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 172400.0,
      "end_time": 176816.0,
      "text": "And it turns out that climate was one of the causes"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176840.0,
      "end_time": 179536.0,
      "text": "in a long chain of events."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 179560.0,
      "end_time": 182336.0,
      "text": "It actually started back in the 1970s."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 182360.0,
      "end_time": 185216.0,
      "text": "When Assad took control over Syria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 185240.0,
      "end_time": 190376.0,
      "text": "he decided he wanted to be self-sufficient in things like wheat and barley."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 190400.0,
      "end_time": 192560.0,
      "text": "Now, you would like to think"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 192800.0,
      "end_time": 194536.0,
      "text": "that there was somebody in Assad&#39;s office that said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 194560.0,
      "end_time": 197656.0,
      "text": "\"Hey boss, you know, we&#39;re in the eastern Mediterranean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 197680.0,
      "end_time": 201136.0,
      "text": "kind of dry here, maybe not the best idea.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 201160.0,
      "end_time": 202616.0,
      "text": "But I think what happened was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 202640.0,
      "end_time": 206736.0,
      "text": "\"Boss, you are a smart, powerful and handsome man. We&#39;ll get right on it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 206760.0,
      "end_time": 207976.0,
      "text": "And they did."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 208000.0,
      "end_time": 211936.0,
      "text": "So by the &#39;90s, believe it or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 211960.0,
      "end_time": 215376.0,
      "text": "they were actually self-sufficient in food,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 215400.0,
      "end_time": 216976.0,
      "text": "but they did it at a great cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 217000.0,
      "end_time": 218936.0,
      "text": "They did it at a cost of their aquifers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 218960.0,
      "end_time": 221960.0,
      "text": "they did it at a cost of their surface water."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 221120.0,
      "end_time": 223336.0,
      "text": "And of course, there are many nonclimate issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 223360.0,
      "end_time": 225560.0,
      "text": "that also contributed to Syria."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 225800.0,
      "end_time": 226296.0,
      "text": "There was the Iraq War,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 226320.0,
      "end_time": 228736.0,
      "text": "and as you can see by that lower blue line there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 228760.0,
      "end_time": 231976.0,
      "text": "over a million refugees come into the cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 232000.0,
      "end_time": 233736.0,
      "text": "And then about a decade ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 233760.0,
      "end_time": 236896.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s this tremendous heat wave and drought --"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 236920.0,
      "end_time": 238976.0,
      "text": "fingerprints all over that show,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 239000.0,
      "end_time": 242216.0,
      "text": "yes, this is in fact related to the changing climate --"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 242240.0,
      "end_time": 245176.0,
      "text": "has put another three quarters of a million farmers"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 245200.0,
      "end_time": 247950.0,
      "text": "into those same cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 247120.0,
      "end_time": 249600.0,
      "text": "Why? Because they had nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 250200.0,
      "end_time": 253176.0,
      "text": "They had dust. They had dirt. They had nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 253200.0,
      "end_time": 255215.0,
      "text": "So now they&#39;re in the cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 255240.0,
      "end_time": 256656.0,
      "text": "the Iraqis are in the cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 256680.0,
      "end_time": 259776.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s Assad, it&#39;s not like he&#39;s taking care of his people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 259800.0,
      "end_time": 264960.0,
      "text": "and all of a sudden we have just this huge issue here"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 264120.0,
      "end_time": 266376.0,
      "text": "of massive instability"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 266400.0,
      "end_time": 268655.0,
      "text": "and a breeding ground for extremism."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 268680.0,
      "end_time": 270656.0,
      "text": "And this is why in the security community"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 270680.0,
      "end_time": 274376.0,
      "text": "we call climate change a risk to instability."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 274400.0,
      "end_time": 276655.0,
      "text": "It accelerates instability here."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 276680.0,
      "end_time": 279440.0,
      "text": "In plain English, it makes bad places worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 280240.0,
      "end_time": 281896.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s go to another place here."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 281920.0,
      "end_time": 286496.0,
      "text": "Now we&#39;re going to go 2,000 kilometers, or about 1,200 miles, north of Oslo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 286520.0,
      "end_time": 289560.0,
      "text": "only 600 miles from the Pole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 289800.0,
      "end_time": 291616.0,
      "text": "and this is arguably"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 291640.0,
      "end_time": 293895.0,
      "text": "the most strategic island you&#39;ve never heard of."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 293920.0,
      "end_time": 295496.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a place called Svalbard."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 295520.0,
      "end_time": 297736.0,
      "text": "It sits astride the sea lanes"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 297760.0,
      "end_time": 303150.0,
      "text": "that the Russian Northern Fleet needs to get out and go into warmer waters."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 303400.0,
      "end_time": 306160.0,
      "text": "It is also, by virtue of its geography,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 306400.0,
      "end_time": 309576.0,
      "text": "a place where you can control every single polar orbiting satellite"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 309600.0,
      "end_time": 310856.0,
      "text": "on every orbit."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 310880.0,
      "end_time": 313496.0,
      "text": "It is the strategic high ground of space."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 313520.0,
      "end_time": 316775.0,
      "text": "Climate change has greatly reduced the sea ice around here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 316800.0,
      "end_time": 319616.0,
      "text": "greatly increasing human activity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 319640.0,
      "end_time": 321135.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s becoming a flashpoint,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 321160.0,
      "end_time": 323216.0,
      "text": "and in fact the NATO Parliamentary Assembly"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 323240.0,
      "end_time": 326256.0,
      "text": "is going to meet here on Svalbard next month."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 326280.0,
      "end_time": 329150.0,
      "text": "The Russians are very, very unhappy about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 329400.0,
      "end_time": 331696.0,
      "text": "So if you want to find a flashpoint in the Arctic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 331720.0,
      "end_time": 333360.0,
      "text": "look at Svalbard there."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 334440.0,
      "end_time": 336216.0,
      "text": "Now, in the military,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 336240.0,
      "end_time": 338576.0,
      "text": "we have known for decades, if not centuries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 338600.0,
      "end_time": 340616.0,
      "text": "that the time to prepare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 340640.0,
      "end_time": 344376.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s for a hurricane, a typhoon or strategic changes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 344400.0,
      "end_time": 346256.0,
      "text": "is before they hit you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 346280.0,
      "end_time": 347976.0,
      "text": "and Admiral Nimitz was right there."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 348000.0,
      "end_time": 349976.0,
      "text": "That is the time to prepare."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 350000.0,
      "end_time": 352496.0,
      "text": "Fortunately, our Secretary of Defense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 352520.0,
      "end_time": 354760.0,
      "text": "Secretary Mattis, he understands that as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 355600.0,
      "end_time": 358656.0,
      "text": "and what he understands is that climate is a risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 358680.0,
      "end_time": 361136.0,
      "text": "He has said so in his written responses to Congress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 361160.0,
      "end_time": 363296.0,
      "text": "and he says, \"As Secretary of Defense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 363320.0,
      "end_time": 366736.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s my job to manage such risks.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 366760.0,
      "end_time": 370695.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not only the US military that understands this."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 370720.0,
      "end_time": 374256.0,
      "text": "Many of our friends and allies in other navies and other militaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 374280.0,
      "end_time": 378560.0,
      "text": "have very clear-eyed views about the climate risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 378800.0,
      "end_time": 382376.0,
      "text": "And in fact, in 2014, I was honored to speak for a half-a-day seminar"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 382400.0,
      "end_time": 384616.0,
      "text": "at the International Seapower Symposium"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 384640.0,
      "end_time": 387479.0,
      "text": "to 70 heads of navies about this issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 389200.0,
      "end_time": 391776.0,
      "text": "So Winston Churchill is alleged to have said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 391800.0,
      "end_time": 395560.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not sure if he said anything, but he&#39;s alleged to have said"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 395800.0,
      "end_time": 399150.0,
      "text": "that Americans can always be counted upon to do the right thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 399400.0,
      "end_time": 401960.0,
      "text": "after exhausting every other possibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 401120.0,
      "end_time": 402696.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 402720.0,
      "end_time": 404936.0,
      "text": "So I would argue we&#39;re still in the process"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 404960.0,
      "end_time": 406816.0,
      "text": "of exhausting every other possibility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 406840.0,
      "end_time": 409416.0,
      "text": "but I do think we will prevail."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 409440.0,
      "end_time": 410896.0,
      "text": "But I need your help."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 410920.0,
      "end_time": 412176.0,
      "text": "This is my ask."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 412200.0,
      "end_time": 415656.0,
      "text": "I ask not that you take your recycling out on Wednesday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 415680.0,
      "end_time": 418656.0,
      "text": "but that you engage with every business leader,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 418680.0,
      "end_time": 421496.0,
      "text": "every technology leader, every government leader,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 421520.0,
      "end_time": 424960.0,
      "text": "and ask them, \"Ma&#39;am, sir,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 424120.0,
      "end_time": 426800.0,
      "text": "what are you doing to stabilize the climate?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 427520.0,
      "end_time": 429560.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just that simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 429800.0,
      "end_time": 432575.0,
      "text": "Because when enough people care enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 432600.0,
      "end_time": 436176.0,
      "text": "the politicians, most of whom won&#39;t lead on this issue --"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 436200.0,
      "end_time": 437976.0,
      "text": "but they will be led --"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 438000.0,
      "end_time": 439376.0,
      "text": "that will change this."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 439400.0,
      "end_time": 443455.0,
      "text": "Because I can tell you, the ice doesn&#39;t care."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 443480.0,
      "end_time": 445896.0,
      "text": "The ice doesn&#39;t care who&#39;s in the White House."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 445920.0,
      "end_time": 448896.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t care which party controls your congress."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 448920.0,
      "end_time": 451496.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t care which party controls your parliament."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 451520.0,
      "end_time": 452976.0,
      "text": "It just melts."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 453000.0,
      "end_time": 454216.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 454240.0,
      "end_time": 460160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}